{"tid":549283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察學院結業會操 張建宗:示威者態度致警隊壓力大","createTime":"2018-02-03T12:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T04:08:09.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6594f84f2a9e39b78d63255cf5fee2d2b021fd","tid":549283,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"香港警察學院今早在黃竹坑警校舉行結業會操，有36名見習督察及237名學警結業，由政務司司長張建宗檢閱會操。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗致詞時表示，本港社會比過去複雜多變，每年遊行數字，由回歸初的2300宗增至去年超過10000宗，每日平均有30宗遊行示威，需要大量警力維持秩序，增加警隊工作量。同時，參與遊行示威人士的態度日漸激烈，甚至作出挑釁，令警隊承受不少壓力。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又稱，法治精神是本港的核心價值，是賴以成功的基石，及維持本港競爭力不可或缺的元素，警隊致力打擊罪行，保護巿民生命財產，令巿民得以安居樂業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1760636/警察學院結業會操+張建宗%3A警隊壓力大\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1760636%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%83%E6%93%8D%2B%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%253A%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%A7&d=UToFpFtFyYbC3xaLCe0vqp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a9f701b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1760636/警察學院結業會操+張建宗%3A警隊壓力大</a>"},{"pid":"47ff79e2fccef1523c4645d4aae79e459e9b3f11","tid":549283,"uid":27664,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"有邊份工冇壓力呀屌你政府"},{"pid":"13f1c673277a1817effeac6fe6d89448eb55f6dc","tid":549283,"uid":62837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"帶頭破壞法治精神 咪你個政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc7fdd6afff0c56c56994e4017e77e5e7aae4aa","tid":549283,"uid":20227,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecf2cb1baadae6a4d471f8559dc57715003f8195","tid":549283,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"又係沾中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/